description: Juliette March has has some impressive moments this season. She's one of the smaller combatants on the roster but she packs a punch. This is Sasha Princess Banks first singles match for U/S. She's shown some spunk in this season's tag matches. These two girls are some of the scrappiest girls we have. They are both stubborn and horny.
title: Two feisty Rookies go at it. One Reigns Supreme. One Fucks the loser
